T21:37:23.000Z","msg":"但角蛋白好似都係電眼睫毛既一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有朋友出去整完一開始幾靚，之後開始傷，啲睫毛彎向唔同角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己個美睫師都建議唔好整角蛋白，傷咗起碼半年先養得返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申佢已經整得唔平"},{"pid":"a520bb598c6acae4b50a8008442026e8d5c1af4a","tid":1404303,"uid":299326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e832cd9bf46fbdbeccfa7ee0cb2c374d573a88","tid":1404303,"uid":50154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"前排喺ig睇到間接眼睫毛廣告，天生眼柒又未整過既我就突然間好想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左佢好多做完效果相都好好，又有試做優惠就拿拿臨走左去book，上到去其實個環鏡同服務態度都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身book左山茶花，但美睫師都推介左平啲既日式單根，因為首次做會易接受啲。<br />\n<br />\n咁佢個美睫師手勢都溫柔，令我差啲瞓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但點解無瞓到呢？因為佢本身就話預1.5至2個鐘做一個客，但佢做左唔夠一個鐘就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁無咩既，快手姐，做出黎效果都ok。<br />\n整完番屋企，我八個鐘都無濕水，夾起埋頭髮做自己野，確保無野會掂到睫毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知過左成晚照鏡，無啦啦已經甩左兩條喺臉上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要我用睫毛梳一梳，甩左條入眼，差啲拎唔番出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但公道啲諗，會唔會係我原生睫毛新陳代謝甩左咋？<br />\n點知今朝一起身<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5V3A5Ka.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5V3A5Ka.png&h=141428eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺塊面同床上收集到呢一堆毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條條都無連原生毛甩<br />\n而家我右眼前半部啲假毛甩哂咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試做都唔洗差到咁啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"因為條友痴得衰  或者膠水唔得"},{"pid":"435856ff8e005527d58b4bb38042504d082bddb5","tid":1404303,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0b2dee0dff44024ff77ebf8d5de61b4ed3b505","tid":1404303,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"電咪算😱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"男人老狗你又知呢啲嘢嘅？"},{"pid":"f9ef54862a6449c413bd89cfbc2f6cb29b096fb0","tid":1404303,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"435856ff8e005527d58b4bb38042504d082bddb5","tid":1404303,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0b2dee0dff44024ff77ebf8d5de61b4ed3b505","tid":1404303,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"電咪算😱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"男人老狗你又知呢啲嘢嘅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:37:01.000Z","msg":"角蛋白"},{"pid":"235315eef7e464a5da9d674a7bcad0dc561004e8","tid":1404303,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff306030b6dc89a88ad2029a0bcd71f81760af1","tid":1404303,"uid":41399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30dc480318b69799d64eda25c1da8f69c728ac27","tid":1404303,"uid":199858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"做角蛋白啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:37:23.000Z","msg":"但角蛋白好似都係電眼睫毛既一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有朋友出去整完一開始幾靚，之後開始傷，啲睫毛彎向唔同角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己個美睫師都建議唔好整角蛋白，傷咗起碼半年先養得返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申佢已經整得唔平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"請問係邊間整得唔好？開少少名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj